{{TA|G1=Electronics}}[[File:Gluehlampe_01_KMJ.png|thumb]]

'''A型灯泡'''（{{lang-en|'''A-series light bulb'''}}），指的是一种“经典”的梨形[[电灯泡|电灯泡]]，大多配有[[爱迪生螺口|爱迪生螺口]]底座。自20世纪早期起，此类灯泡一直是最常见的日常电灯。A型灯泡的型号后面的数字表示其最宽处直径，在北美按{{convert|1/8|in}}为一单位计算，<ref name=Grainger>{{cite web|trans-title=灯泡大小及特征对比|title=Lamp Size and Comparison Features|publisher=WW Grainger Inc.|quote=A=Arbitrary ''[...]'' Lamp size (maximum lamp diameter) is expressed by a number representing eighths of an inch.|url=http://www.grainger.com/tps/lighting_lamp_size_and_feature_comparison.pdf|format=PDF|language=en|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924023409/http://www.grainger.com/tps/lighting_lamp_size_and_feature_comparison.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Superior/>在欧洲、印度则以[[毫米|毫米]]计。<ref name="IS 14897:2000">{{cite web|title=https://archive.org/details/gov.in.is.14897.2000|accessdate=21 March 2017|quote=A bulb shape having a spherical and [''sic''; end?] section that is joined to the neck by a radius [...] A60: An “A” shape bulb with a nominal major diameter of 60 mm.}}</ref><ref name=Eagle>{{cite web|trans-title=灯泡大小及尺寸详解|title=Light Bulb Shapes and Sizes Explained|work=LED University|publisher=EagleLight|url=http://www.eaglelight.com/category/lighting_tutorials.bulb_shapes/|quote='A' type bulb shapes are standard house hold light bulbs. The number after the bulb shape is the number of eighths of an inch in diameter. For non-imperial measured bulbs the number following the bulb shape is the number of centimeters [''sic''] at the widest point of the bulb. Standard bulb sizes include A19 for imperial measurements and A60 for a slightly smaller metric measured bulb.|language=en|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-date=2017-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121043242/http://www.eaglelight.com/category/lighting_tutorials.bulb_shapes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=GLS_LED_A60>{{cite web|title=LED Start GLS: 40, 60, 75 & 90w equivalents|url=http://www.gelighting.com/LightingWeb/emea/images/LED_Start_GLS_Data_Sheet_EN_tcm181-83867.pdf|publisher=通用电气照明|accessdate=2017-03-21|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321170033/http://www.gelighting.com/LightingWeb/emea/images/LED_Start_GLS_Data_Sheet_EN_tcm181-83867.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==形状==
[[File:Philips_LED_bulbs.jpg|thumb]]

最常用的A型灯泡是A19灯泡，<ref name=Superior>{{cite web |trans-title=灯泡参考指南 |title=Light Bulb Reference Guide |publisher=Superior Lighting |url=http://www.superiorlighting.com/BULB_REFERENCE_GUIDE_s/218.htm |quote=The letter indicates the shape of the bulb and the number relates to the diameter of the bulb in eighths of an inch. The most commonly used household bulb is the A-19. |language=en |accessdate=2017-03-13 |archive-date=2016-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227223154/http://www.superiorlighting.com/BULB_REFERENCE_GUIDE_s/218.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>其最宽处直径为{{convert|19/8|in}}，因此在[[公制|公制]]单位中也叫做A60灯泡。<ref name=Eagle/>一般的A19灯泡长{{convert|4+3/8|in|cm}}。

按照美国ANSI C79.1-2002、印度IS 14897:2000<ref name="IS 14897:2000"/>、日本JIS C 7710:1988<ref name="JIS C 7710:1988">{{cite web|title=JIS C 7710:1988 電球類ガラス管球の形式の表し方|url=http://kikakurui.com/c7/C7710-1988-01.html|accessdate=2017-03-21|language=ja|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111224419/http://kikakurui.com/c7/C7710-1988-01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>定义，A型灯泡符合“由一个末端的球形和一段曲面相切连接到灯泡颈部”形成的形状，其中曲面本身的[[曲率半径|曲率半径]]指向灯泡外部，且大于灯泡末端球的半径。美国[[能源之星|能源之星]]认证对于节能万向灯泡的要求则仅有“符合相应ANSI形状的最大半径、最小长度、最长长度”一点。<ref name="ES2.0">{{cite web|title=ENERGY STAR Eligibility Criteria Version 2.0, Rev. Oct-2016|url=https://www.energystar.gov/sites/default/files/ENERGY%20STAR%20Lamps%20V2_0%20Revised%20OCT-2016_1.pdf|accessdate=2017-03-21|language=en|quote=Lamp shall comply with ANSI minimum overall length (min OAL), maximum overall length (MOL) and maximum lamp diameter values, where they exist|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321165451/https://www.energystar.gov/sites/default/files/ENERGY%20STAR%20Lamps%20V2_0%20Revised%20OCT-2016_1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|at=14.1}}

==接口==
{{see also|爱迪生螺旋}}
A型灯泡常配有约{{convert|1|in}}长的E26（直径26毫米，100–120V）或E27（直径27毫米，220–240V）螺口。在[[英国|英国]]及[[英联邦|英联邦]]国家的老式灯具上也可见到使用B22拧口的A型灯泡。<ref name="tuxgraphic-size">{{cite web|trans-title=灯具及灯泡尺寸|title=Light fixtures and light bulb sizes|url=http://www.tuxgraphics.org/electronics/powersockets/light_bulb_types.html|website=www.tuxgraphics.org|accessdate=2017-02-28|language=en|archive-date=2017-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425114110/http://www.tuxgraphics.org/electronics/powersockets/light_bulb_types.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==类型==
[[File:Led-lampa.jpg|thumb]]
历史上大部分A型灯泡都是[[白熾燈|白熾燈]]，但现在也有采用较新的电灯技术（如[[节能灯|节能灯]]、[[發光二極管燈|LED灯]]等）的版本，用以替代相应尺寸的白炽灯。<ref name=Eagle/><ref name=GLS_LED_A60/>

